headline.main: Italy's Role in "New Order"; 19 ITALIAN GUILDS GET NEW LEADERS

lead_paragraph: ROME, Oct. 25 -- Italy expects to have an equal partnership in the new European order and will not abandon her industrial structure for agriculture, according to Virginio Gayda in an editorial in the Giornale d'Italia discussing the visit of the German Economic Minister, Dr. Walther Funk, to Rome.
